  "detailed_description": "Lost In Failures is an <strong>action</strong>, <strong>survival</strong> and <strong>adventure</strong> game set in a <strong>living</strong>, <strong>rich</strong> and <strong>challenging</strong> open world. In the work you control <strong>David</strong>, a character who had a normal life, but suddenly woke up on an unknown beach surrounded by a dense forest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0cdc1c88a829fa289c121d1d995ddb7e.poster.avif?t=1711103012\" width=640 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0cdc1c88a829fa289c121d1d995ddb7e.webm?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0cdc1c88a829fa289c121d1d995ddb7e.mp4?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The region has many <strong>mysteries</strong> and <strong>enemies</strong> that will do whatever is necessary to kill you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/40abbd78914d09413a71c0b0d50620b8.poster.avif?t=1711103012\" width=640 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/40abbd78914d09413a71c0b0d50620b8.webm?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/40abbd78914d09413a71c0b0d50620b8.mp4?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>His goal is to regain his <strong>normal life</strong>, for this, he will have the help of <strong>Hades</strong>, a strange man who claims to have the answers to the problems David is facing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0b39567c4401faa5e087d96c156673bb.poster.avif?t=1711103012\" width=640 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0b39567c4401faa5e087d96c156673bb.webm?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0b39567c4401faa5e087d96c156673bb.mp4?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The player will need to understand what is happening to the world around them, <strong>explore</strong> and <strong>fight</strong> with all their might to save your life!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/ec9e4fb27ba7dba3550a985184a6ef57.poster.avif?t=1711103012\" width=640 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/ec9e4fb27ba7dba3550a985184a6ef57.webm?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/ec9e4fb27ba7dba3550a985184a6ef57.mp4?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The world of the work allows you to <strong>craft</strong> items and equipments, <strong>hunt</strong> various species of wild animals, <strong>explore</strong> caves and structures, <strong>invade</strong> enemy occupations, <strong>evolve</strong> the character's skills and much more.<br><br><strong><u>Game mechanics:</u></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Management of life, stamina, hunger and thirst;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Manufacture of items and equipment;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun and challenging combat;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use and domestication of horses;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Animal hunting;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Construction of structures for the camp;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Evolution of skills.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Lost In Failures is an <strong>action</strong>, <strong>survival</strong> and <strong>adventure</strong> game set in a <strong>living</strong>, <strong>rich</strong> and <strong>challenging</strong> open world. In the work you control <strong>David</strong>, a character who had a normal life, but suddenly woke up on an unknown beach surrounded by a dense forest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0cdc1c88a829fa289c121d1d995ddb7e.poster.avif?t=1711103012\" width=640 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0cdc1c88a829fa289c121d1d995ddb7e.webm?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/0cdc1c88a829fa289c121d1d995ddb7e.mp4?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The region has many <strong>mysteries</strong> and <strong>enemies</strong> that will do whatever is necessary to kill you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/40abbd78914d09413a71c0b0d50620b8.poster.avif?t=1711103012\" width=640 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/40abbd78914d09413a71c0b0d50620b8.webm?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813250/extras/40abbd78914d09413a71c0b0d50620b8.mp4?t=1711103012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>His goal is to regain his <strong>normal life</strong>, for this, he will have the help of <strong>Hades</strong>, a strange man who claims to have the answers to the problems David is facing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_c