tication of horses;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Animal hunting;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Construction of structures for the camp;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Evolution of skills.</li></ul>",
